---
import App from "@venn/App.vue";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ChatApp from "@venn/ChatApp.vue";
---

<Layout
	title="Hoogly | Reinventing Employee Engagement"
	description="AI-powered employee engagement platform that's 10X better than surveys. Transform your workplace culture with Venn AI."
	type="website"
>
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="hero hero-fullscreen">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<div class="hero-text">
					<div
						class="hero-title"
						style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.2em; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;"
					>
						<div class="hero-title-align" style="display: block;">
							<span class="hero-title-text">Tired of </span><span
								class="hero-highlight"
								><span class="hero-highlight-text">meh</span
								></span
							><span class="hero-title-text">
								survey results?</span
							>
						</div>
						<div class="hero-title-second-line">
							So are your employees.
						</div>
					</div>
					<div
						class="hero-subtitle"
						style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 400; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5em; padding-top: 1rem; line-height: 30px;"
					>
						10x better insights, powered by AI.
					</div>
					<div
						style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap;"
					>
						<a
							href="https://calendly.com/hoogly/30min"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer"
							class="btn book-demo-btn"
							style="font-size: 1.5rem; padding: 1rem 2.5rem; border-radius: 71px; background: white; color: #23221F; border: 1.5px solid #e0e0e0; transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s, background 0.2s;"
						>
							Book a Demo
						</a>
						<a
							href="/get-started?button-label=Start Free&page-source=homepage"
							class="btn btn-accent"
							style="font-size: 1.5rem; padding: 1rem 3.5rem; border-radius: 71px;"
						>
							Start Free
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<ChatApp client:only="vue" variant="mini" />
			</div>
			<div
				class="hero-flip-image"
				style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-end; margin-top: 4.5rem;"
			>
				<img
					id="heroFlipImage"
					src="/images/new%20dash.png"
					alt="Dashboard Hero"
					style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 1162.33px; min-width: 0; border-radius: 18px; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(44, 41, 80, 0.12);"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Anonymous 1:1 Conversations Section -->
	<section class="anonymous-ai-section section-gradient">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="anonymous-ai-content">
				<img
					src="/images/Section 1.png"
					alt="Section 1"
					class="anonymous-ai-image animate-in"
					style="width: 420px; max-width: 100%;"
				/>
				<div class="anonymous-ai-text">
					<h2
						class="anonymous-ai-headline"
						style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 400;"
					>
						<span class="hero-highlight"
							><span class="hero-highlight-text">Anonymous</span
							></span
						><span>
							1:1 conversations that uncover what surveys miss</span>
					</h2>
					<p
						class="anonymous-ai-subheadline"
						style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 400;"
					>
						Surveys give you answers people think they're supposed
						to say. Venn, our AI culture coach, chats privately with
						every employee—so they can speak freely and be truly
						heard. You don't just collect data. You unlock trust.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Spot the Risks Section -->
	<section class="anonymous-ai-section anonymous-ai-section-tight">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="anonymous-ai-content">
				<div class="anonymous-ai-text">
					<h2
						class="anonymous-ai-headline"
						style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 400;"
					>
						<span class="hero-highlight"
							><span class="hero-highlight-text"
								>Emotions are messy.</span
							></span
						> We make sense of them — at scale.
					</h2>
					<p
						class="anonymous-ai-subheadline"
						style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 400;"
					>
						Venn doesn't just listen—he reads between the lines. By
						analysing tone, patterns, and emerging themes across
						every conversation, our AI surfaces what's really going
						on beneath the surface. So instead of noise, you get
						clarity on what to act on now—and what to watch next.
					</p>
				</div>
				<img
					src="/images/Section 2.png"
					alt="Section 2"
					class="anonymous-ai-image animate-in"
					style="width: 420px; max-width: 100%;"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Spot the Risks Section -->
	<section
		class="anonymous-ai-section anonymous-ai-section-tight section-gradient"
	>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="anonymous-ai-content">
				<img
					src="/images/Section 3.png"
					alt="Section 3"
					class="anonymous-ai-image animate-in"
					style="width: 420px; max-width: 100%;"
				/>
				<div class="anonymous-ai-text">
					<h2
						class="anonymous-ai-headline"
						style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 400;"
					>
						From insight to impact — with <span
							class="hero-highlight"
							><span class="hero-highlight-text"
								>AI at your side</span
							></span>
					</h2>
					<p
						class="anonymous-ai-subheadline"
						style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 400;"
					>
						Venn turns honest feedback into clear action plans, like
						reducing meeting overload or rolling out a mentoring
						program. Then, our AI agents help you follow through:
						nudging the right people, syncing calendars, and
						tracking progress.
						<br /><br />
						Because culture change doesn't happen in a spreadsheet. It
						needs action.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Spot the Risks Section -->
	<section class="anonymous-ai-section anonymous-ai-section-tight">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="anonymous-ai-content">
				<div class="anonymous-ai-text">
					<h2
						class="anonymous-ai-headline"
						style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 400;"
					>
						Celebrate progress, build <span class="hero-highlight"
							><span class="hero-highlight-text">trust</span
							></span>
					</h2>
					<p
						class="anonymous-ai-subheadline"
						style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 400;"
					>
						In the past, employees gave feedback, but never saw what
						changed. With Hoogly, every positive action—big or
						small—is surfaced and celebrated across the team. It
						closes the loop, shows that leaders care, and encourages
						even more open, constructive feedback next time.
					</p>
				</div>
				<img
					src="/images/Section 4.png"
					alt="Section 4"
					class="anonymous-ai-image animate-in"
					style="width: 420px; max-width: 100%;"
				/>
			</div>
			<div class="integrations-subsection" style="margin-top: 4rem;">
				<h3
					class="integrations-title animate-in"
					style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; color: #2d2a58; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: var(--font-size-lg);"
				>
					Integrates with:
				</h3>
				<div
					class="integration-logos animate-in"
					id="integratesWithCarousel"
					style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 4rem; flex-wrap: wrap;"
				>
					<div class="logos-track" style="display: flex; gap: 4rem;">
						<img
							src="/images/slack-logo.png"
							alt="Slack"
							style="height: 35px; filter: grayscale(1) opacity(0.7);"
						/>
						<img
							src="/images/teams-logo.png"
							alt="Microsoft Teams"
							style="height: 44px; width: auto; filter: grayscale(1) opacity(0.7);"
						/>
						<img
							src="/images/employment-hero.png"
							alt="Employment Hero"
							style="height: 24px; width: auto; margin-top: 6px; filter: grayscale(1) opacity(0.7);"
						/>
						<img
							src="/images/bamboohr-logo.png"
							alt="BambooHR"
							style="height: 35px; filter: grayscale(1) opacity(0.7);"
						/>
						<img
							src="/images/workday-logo.png"
							alt="Workday"
							style="height: 35px; filter: grayscale(1) opacity(0.7);"
						/>
					</div>
					<div class="logos-track" style="display: flex; gap: 4rem;">
						<img
							src="/images/slack-logo.png"
							alt="Slack"
							style="height: 35px; filter: grayscale(1) opacity(0.7);"
						/>
						<img
							src="/images/teams-logo.png"
							alt="Microsoft Teams"
							style="height: 44px; width: auto; filter: grayscale(1) opacity(0.7);"
						/>
						<img
							src="/images/employment-hero.png"
							alt="Employment Hero"
							style="height: 24px; width: auto; margin-top: 6px; filter: grayscale(1) opacity(0.7);"
						/>
						<img
							src="/images/bamboohr-logo.png"
							alt="BambooHR"
							style="height: 35px; filter: grayscale(1) opacity(0.7);"
						/>
						<img
							src="/images/workday-logo.png"
							alt="Workday"
							style="height: 35px; filter: grayscale(1) opacity(0.7);"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Testimonial Section -->
	<section
		class="testimonial-section"
		style="background: #FCF4E3; border-radius: 2rem; max-width: 1200px; margin: 4rem auto 9rem auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(44,41,80,0.04); position: relative;"
	>
		<div
			class="testimonial-content"
			style="width: 100%; padding: 3.5rem 2rem 3rem 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center;"
		>
			<p
				style="font-family: 'Outfit', serif; font-size: 1.65rem; color: #23221F; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; line-height: 1.3; max-width: 600px; font-style: italic;"
			>
				“Hoogly has shown building a company culture in a remote
				environment is not just possible but an opportunity to fix some
				of the flaws of the traditional workplace model.”
			</p>
			<div
				style="margin-top: auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;"
			>
				<div
					style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #23221F; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 500;"
				>
					Sérgio Godinho
				</div>
				<div
					style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #888; font-size: 1.1rem;"
				>
					Lisbon, Portugal
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Built by the People Behind the People Section -->
	<section
		class="built-by-section"
		style="background: #E8E6FF; padding: var(--space-20) 0; width: 100vw; margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);"
	>
		<div class="container">
			<div style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
				<h2
					style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: var(--font-size-4xl); margin-bottom: 3rem; color: #23221F; text-align: center;"
				>
					Built by people from some of the most iconic workplaces
				</h2>
				<p
					style="font-size: var(--font-size-xl); color: #23221F; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.6;"
				>
					We're ex-TikTok, Airbnb, Meta, Mangahigh, hipages, and we've
					seen what makes culture click (and what breaks it).
				</p>
				<div
					class="integration-logos animate-in"
					id="builtByPeopleCarousel"
					style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: nowrap; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;"
				>
					<div class="logos-track" style="display: flex; gap: 2rem;">
						<img
							src="/images/Home/tiktok_PNG22.png"
							alt="TikTok"
							style="height: 72px; width: auto; vertical-align: middle; filter: brightness(0) saturate(100%) invert(10%) sepia(7%) saturate(7500%) hue-rotate(205deg) brightness(90%) contrast(110%);"
						/>
						<img
							src="/images/Home/airbnb-logo.png"
							alt="Airbnb"
							style="height: 72px; width: auto; vertical-align: middle; filter: brightness(0) saturate(100%) invert(10%) sepia(7%) saturate(7500%) hue-rotate(205deg) brightness(90%) contrast(110%);"
						/>
						<img
							src="/images/Home/Meta-Logo.png"
							alt="Meta"
							style="height: 72px; width: auto; vertical-align: middle; filter: brightness(0) saturate(100%) invert(10%) sepia(7%) saturate(7500%) hue-rotate(205deg) brightness(90%) contrast(110%);"
						/>
						<img
							src="/images/Home/mangahighlogo.png"
							alt="Mangahigh"
							style="height: 120px; width: auto; vertical-align: middle; margin-top: -24px; filter: brightness(0) saturate(100%) invert(10%) sepia(7%) saturate(7500%) hue-rotate(205deg) brightness(90%) contrast(110%);"
						/>
						<img
							src="/images/Home/Hipages_logo.png"
							alt="hipages"
							style="height: 72px; width: auto; vertical-align: middle; filter: brightness(0) saturate(100%) invert(10%) sepia(7%) saturate(7500%) hue-rotate(205deg) brightness(90%) contrast(110%);"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>
				<a
					href="/about"
					class="btn btn-accent"
					style="font-size: 1.35rem; padding: 1.25rem 2.75rem; border-radius: 71px; margin-bottom: 2rem; display: inline-block;"
					>Meet the team</a
				>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- FAQ Section -->
	<section
		class="faq-section"
		style="background: white; padding: var(--space-20) 0; width: 100vw; margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);"
	>
		<div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
			<div
				class="faq-section"
				style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; width: 100%;"
			>
				<h2
					style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; color: #23221F; margin-bottom: 2rem; margin-top: 0;"
				>
					Frequently Asked Questions
				</h2>
				<style>
					.faq-section {
						width: 100%;
						padding-top: var(--space-16, 16px);
						display: flex;
						flex-direction: column;
						justify-content: center;
						align-items: flex-start;
						gap: 0;
						align-self: stretch;
					}
					.faq-item {
						width: 100%;
						border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
						padding: 0;
						margin-top: 0;
						margin-bottom: 1rem;
					}
					.faq-item:last-child {
						margin-bottom: 0;
					}
					.faq-summary {
						font-size: 1.35rem;
						font-weight: 500;
						font-family: "Outfit", sans-serif;
						color: #23221f;
						cursor: pointer;
						outline: none;
						display: flex;
						align-items: center;
						justify-content: space-between;
						padding: 1.2rem 0 0.4rem 0;
						margin-top: 0;
						transition: background 0.2s;
						line-height: 1.2;
						min-height: 3rem;
					}
					.faq-summary span:first-child {
						display: flex;
						align-items: center;
						line-height: 1.4;
					}
					.faq-arrow {
						display: flex;
						width: 32px;
						height: 32px;
						padding: 0;
						justify-content: center;
						align-items: center;
						gap: 6px;
						flex-shrink: 0;
						border-radius: 64px;
						background: #d0ccff;
						backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
						transition: background 0.2s;
					}
					.faq-arrow svg {
						width: 26px;
						height: 26px;
						transition: transform 0.3s ease;
						display: block;
					}
					.faq-item.open .faq-arrow svg {
						transform: rotate(180deg);
					}
					.faq-answer {
						color: #444;
						font-size: 1.08rem;
						font-weight: 400;
						margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
						padding-left: 0;
						padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
						padding-right: 2.5rem;
						padding-top: 0;
						text-align: left;
						line-height: 1.7;
						max-height: 0;
						opacity: 0;
						overflow: hidden;
						transition:
							max-height 0.4s ease,
							opacity 0.4s ease;
					}
					.faq-item.open .faq-answer {
						opacity: 1;
						max-height: 500px;
					}
					@media (max-width: 600px) {
						.hero-subtitle {
							display: block !important;
							-webkit-line-clamp: unset !important;
							-webkit-box-orient: unset !important;
							overflow: visible !important;
							text-overflow: unset !important;
							min-height: unset !important;
							padding: 0 1rem !important;
							font-size: 1.1rem !important;
						}
						.hero-section-awards img {
							height: 80px !important;
						}
					}
					.book-demo-btn:hover,
					.book-demo-btn:focus {
						outline: none;
						border-width: 1.5px;
						border-color: #23221f !important;
						background: white !important;
						color: #23221f !important;
					}
				</style>
				<div class="faq-item">
					<div class="faq-summary">
						<span>How do I get support from Hoogly?</span>
						<span class="faq-arrow">
							<svg
								width="26"
								height="26"
								viewBox="0 0 20 20"
								fill="none"
								xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
								style="display: block; margin: auto;"
							>
								<path
									d="M7 8l3 3 3-3"
									stroke="#23221F"
									stroke-width="1.4"
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
							</svg>
						</span>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						You can email us at <a
							href="mailto:support@hoogly.com"
							style="color: #6c63ff; text-decoration: underline;"
							>support@hoogly.com</a
						> and our team will get back to you as soon as possible.
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="faq-item">
					<div class="faq-summary">
						<span>What service does Hoogly provide?</span>
						<span class="faq-arrow">
							<svg
								width="26"
								height="26"
								viewBox="0 0 20 20"
								fill="none"
								xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
								style="display: block; margin: auto;"
								><path
									d="M7 8l3 3 3-3"
									stroke="#23221F"
									stroke-width="1.4"
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg
							>
						</span>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						Hoogly replaces clunky, one-off surveys with friendly AI
						conversations. By gathering insight continuously, our
						platform turns employee voices into clear, actionable
						guidance and then coaches leaders to translate that
						guidance into meaningful change—so engagement rises and
						everyone feels they belong.
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="faq-item">
					<div class="faq-summary">
						<span>How do colleagues access Hoogly?</span>
						<span class="faq-arrow">
							<svg
								width="26"
								height="26"
								viewBox="0 0 20 20"
								fill="none"
								xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
								style="display: block; margin: auto;"
								><path
									d="M7 8l3 3 3-3"
									stroke="#23221F"
									stroke-width="1.4"
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg
							>
						</span>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						Employees simply sign in with Google or Microsoft SSO
						and start using our stand-alone app (iOS, Android, or
						any browser). Smart nudges appear in Slack or Microsoft
						Teams, reminding them whenever a new survey is due.
						Because it's easy to set up, most organisations are
						live—first pulse and all—within about 30 minutes.
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="faq-item">
					<div class="faq-summary">
						<span
							>How is Hoogly different from other
							employee-engagement tools?</span
						>
						<span class="faq-arrow">
							<svg
								width="26"
								height="26"
								viewBox="0 0 20 20"
								fill="none"
								xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
								style="display: block; margin: auto;"
								><path
									d="M7 8l3 3 3-3"
									stroke="#23221F"
									stroke-width="1.4"
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg
							>
						</span>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						We don't just measure culture—we help build it.
						Listening is our super-power: AI-powered conversations
						surface insights up to 10 × richer than old-school
						surveys. Those insights become personalised performance
						coaching for every employee, leader, and HR partner,
						while our Relational Intelligence engine suggests ways
						colleagues can collaborate even better. All of this
						happens under strict privacy safeguards, so feedback
						stays confidential and only the right people see the
						right data.
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="faq-item">
					<div class="faq-summary">
						<span
							>What's your pricing model—any setup fees or
							contract requirements?</span
						>
						<span class="faq-arrow">
							<svg
								width="26"
								height="26"
								viewBox="0 0 20 20"
								fill="none"
								xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
								style="display: block; margin: auto;"
								><path
									d="M7 8l3 3 3-3"
									stroke="#23221F"
									stroke-width="1.4"
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg
							>
						</span>
